### task-06.outline
Task: 06
Title: RunFusionUseCase ensemble overhaul
Phase: 2
Route: full
Slice: Slice 3 (Use Case)
Dependencies: 03 (PanelRunner), 04 (JudgeStep), 05 (SynthesizeStep)
Scope: Replace the existing passthrough body in RunFusionUseCase with full ensemble orchestration: panel (via PanelRunner) → progress event → judge (via JudgeStep) → progress event → synthesis (via SynthesizeStep) → done event. The constructor now takes PanelRunner, JudgeStep, SynthesizeStep instead of a single ChatModelPort. Yields progress events during panel and judge phases. The use case resolves models from ConfigPort and manages the full pipeline lifecycle including failed_models propagation and timeout passthrough. Modify existing run-fusion-use-case.test.ts to match the new constructor and test the ensemble pipeline with stubbed PanelRunner, JudgeStep, and SynthesizeStep.
Acceptance Criteria: AC-4 (orchestrates full pipeline), AC-9 (end-to-end grounding), AC-12 (timeout passthrough), AC-13 (full stage logging), AC-14 (application tests)
NFRs: NFR-1, NFR-5 (graceful degradation orchestration), NFR-7 (per-stage logging calls)
Gate Criteria: Phase 2 Gate 1 (ensemble response references panel + judge), Phase 2 Gate 2 (graceful degradation path exercised), Phase 3 Gate 2 (timeout cancellation plumbing)
Files:
  - src/application/usecases/run-fusion-use-case.ts (MODIFY) — Replace constructor to accept (panelRunner: PanelRunner, judgeStep: JudgeStep, synthesizeStep: SynthesizeStep, configPort: ConfigPort, loggerPort: LoggerPort, clockPort: ClockPort). Replace runFusion() body with ensemble pipeline: resolve panel/judge/synthesizer models from ConfigPort → run PanelRunner → yield progress('panel') → run JudgeStep with null guard on judgeModel → yield progress('judge') → run SynthesizeStep → yield content/stop → yield done with usage and failedModels. Propagate AbortSignal/timeout from request to panel and judge calls.
  - src/application/usecases/run-fusion-use-case.test.ts (MODIFY) — Replace existing passthrough tests with ensemble pipeline tests: full happy path with stubbed PanelRunner/JudgeStep/SynthesizeStep, partial panel failure reported in done event, judge returning null degrades gracefully, synthesize called with correct panel results, progress events emitted. Preserve existing stubs for ConfigPort, LoggerPort, ClockPort. Adapt to new constructor signature.
